cs-fuuka-yamagishi.1079.description:
Your favorite navigator from the "Persona" franchise is ready for a new adventure! Play as Fuuka and jump, punch, even fly your way to get 120 power stars and save The Mushroom Kingdom!

This mod was the collective effort and journey of a lot of different people - and i'd like to take the time to properly thank EVERYONE who helped contribute into the creation of the mod. So thank you to:

@takebafan
 on twitter (me!) - for reaching out to everyone and bringing this project to reality - as well as do all the coding for the character select menu, and all the voice line stuff!

TrixieBun
 on BlueSky - who did all the really really hard stuff that I was too stupid to figure out! You laid a fantastic foundation for this mod and NONE of this would have happened without you. Thank you for giving me this opportunity (and permission) to refine this mod and bring it out to the public for all to use and have fun with!

@AccurstMaiden
 on twitter - Who contacted me and gave me an earlier build of the mod, as well as pointing me into the correct direction to the original creator of the foundation. You laid the stepping stones to the end path, and were super fun to talk to as well!

@Xeeoh
 on twitter - Who made the custom life icon sprite and lemon health bar for Fuuka - as well as just help playtest the multiplayer functionality - and just being one of my best friends in the whole wide world! Always supportive of my endeavors. I truly don't deserve you

@SuzieYeung
 the official VA for Fuuka - who (legally) is not at all tied to this project, but I did sample the voice of to use for her!

And finally 
@__Smokin_joe__
 on twitter -  For creating the box fan art utilized on the mod page, as well as just being an incredible friend all around! You truly are so kind for going out of your way to do that

If you plan on showing this mod to others on other websites or utilizing it for content - I would greatly appreciate if you credited me 
@takebafan
 on twitter, as well as included a link to the mod page so all these other wonderful people can be thanked for their hard work!

Thanks and enjoy!

